'''傑夫·麥克勒'''（{{lang-en|Jeffrey Mackler}}，{{bd|？}}）是一名出生于[[美國|美國]][[圣弗朗西斯科|圣弗朗西斯科]]的活動家，也是[[托洛茨基主义|托洛茨基主义]]政黨[[社会主义行动_(美国)|社會主義行動]]的全國書記<ref name="Delgado">{{cite news|url=http://leftvoice.org/The-Class-Line-in-Elections-Is-the-Principled-Issue|title=The Class Line in Elections Is the Principled Issue|last=Delgado|first=Moisés|work=LeftVoice.org|accessdate=27 March 2017|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813152418/https://www.leftvoice.org/The-Class-Line-in-Elections-Is-the-Principled-Issue|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾代表該黨參選{{le|2006年加利福尼亞州美國參議院議員選舉|2006 United States Senate election in California|2006年}}[[美國參議院|美國參議院]][[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]代表議員<ref>{{cite web|url=https://socialistaction.org/2006/09/24/news-from-the-jeff-mackler-for-u-s-senate-campaign/|title=News From the Jeff Mackler for U.S. Senate Campaign|website=SocialistAction.org|last1=Grant|first1=Amy|date=September 24, 2006|accessdate=January 16, 2020|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128051548/https://socialistaction.org/2006/09/24/news-from-the-jeff-mackler-for-u-s-senate-campaign/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同年亦成為該黨的[[2016年美國總統選舉|總統選舉]]的[[美國總統|總統]]候選人<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nowtoronto.com/events/rally-for-the-socialist-candidate-for-us-president/|title=Rally For The Socialist Candidate For United States President, Jeff Mackler|website=[[Now_(newspaper)|Now Toronto]]|date=October 21, 2019|accessdate=January 16, 2020|archive-date=2020-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116065002/https://nowtoronto.com/events/rally-for-the-socialist-candidate-for-us-president/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，得到[[自由社會黨|自由社會黨]]的支持<ref name="Cornish">{{cite news|url=http://www.socialism.com/drupal-6.8/articles/america-first-revival-fascist-ideology|title=America First: Revival of a fascist ideology|last=Cornish|first=Megan|date=October 2016|publisher=socialism.com|accessdate=27 March 2017|archive-date=2017-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170818184411/http://www.socialism.com/drupal-6.8/articles/america-first-revival-fascist-ideology|dead-url=no}}</ref>；而兩次選舉中，麥克勒都只能手寫獲得選票<ref>{{cite news|url=https://socialistaction.org/2016/06/26/interview-with-socialist-presidential-candidate-jeff-mackler/|title=Interview with Socialist Action's presidential candidate, Jeff Mackler|website=SocialistAction.org|last=Baker|first=Nick|date=June 26, 2016|accessdate=27 March 2017|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202190610/https://socialistaction.org/2016/06/26/interview-with-socialist-presidential-candidate-jeff-mackler/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年，他宣布代表社會主義行動競逐[[2020年美國總統選舉|2020年美國總統選舉]]總統職務<ref>{{cite news|url=https://socialistaction.org/2019/05/11/socialist-action-launches-2020-presidential-campaign/|title=Socialist Action launches 2020 presidential campaign|website=SocialistAction.org|last=Baker|first=Nick|date=May 11, 2019|accessdate=20 May 2019|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123011937/https://socialistaction.org/2019/05/11/socialist-action-launches-2020-presidential-campaign/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

麥克勒在{{le|安提阿學院|Antioch College}}畢業後，創立了北加利福尼亞州氣候動員組織，是[[海沃德_(加利福尼亚州)|加利福尼亞州海沃德]][[美國教師聯盟|美國教師聯盟]]的長期教師和工會活動家，也是自由{{le|穆米亞·阿布·賈馬爾|Mumia Abu-Jamal}}的動員主任<ref name=Action2016>{{cite web|url=https://socialistaction.org/2016/06/23/vote-socialist-action-in-2016-jeff-mackler-for-u-s-president/|title=Vote Socialist Action in 2016! Jeff Mackler for U.S. President!|date=June 23, 2016|website=SocialistAction.org|accessdate=27 March 2017|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211081341/https://socialistaction.org/2016/06/23/vote-socialist-action-in-2016-jeff-mackler-for-u-s-president/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

